<%- include("partials/head.ejs") %>

<body class="container-fluid email">
  <div class="container header-image-container">
    <img
      src="<%= cloudinary.url %>/w_768,c_lfill/public/bg/emails-welcome.jpg"
      alt="#WOKEWeekly"
      class="header-image"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="container email-content">
    Hey <%= user.firstname %>! <br /><br />

    Thank you for joining the #WOKEWeekly website. We're very honoured to have
    your support!
    <br /><br />

    Remember, your username is <strong><%= user.username %></strong>. You can
    use your username, as well as this email address, to log in to the website
    from here on out. You are free to change your username at any point in time
    by going on your account page. <br /><br />

    You'll need to verify your account, which can be done simply by clicking the
    button below:

    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="<%= domain %>/account?verify=<%= token %>" class="button">
        Verify Your Account
      </a>
    </div>

    We look forward to your interaction with our site or any other enquiries you
    may have!
    <br /><br />

    Yours truly,<br />
    The #WOKEWeekly Team.
  </div>
</body>

